data.description: Buyer can potentially assume a 2.5% interest rate on the existing mortgage balance! Welcome to your charming ranch-style oasis with convenient location! This delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and character, making it an ideal place to call your own. As you approach you'll immediately notice the well-maintained exterior with a welcoming front porch. Step inside to be greeted by a warm and inviting living room filled with natural light streaming through the windows. The open layout seamlessly connects the living area to the dining room, creating a perfect space for gatherings and entertaining. The spacious kitchen boasts ample cabinet space, making meal preparation a breeze. Three generously sized bedrooms offer comfortable retreats for rest and relaxation. The backyard is a haven featuring a spacious wood deck. The generously sized yard offers endless possibilities for gardening, outdoor activities, or simply unwinding in nature.
